Package com.salesforce.multicloudj.dbbackuprestore.ali

Class AliDBBackupRestore

java.lang.Object
com.salesforce.multicloudj.dbbackuprestore.driver.AbstractDBBackupRestore
com.salesforce.multicloudj.dbbackuprestore.ali.AliDBBackupRestore
All Implemented Interfaces:
Provider, AutoCloseable
@AutoService(AbstractDBBackupRestore.class) public class AliDBBackupRestore extends AbstractDBBackupRestore
Alibaba Cloud implementation of database backup and restore operations. This implementation uses the HBR (Hybrid Backup Recovery) service for TableStore backups.

The HBR service manages TableStore backups through OTS (Open Table Service) snapshots. Backups are created by HBR backup plans and can be restored using the CreateRestoreJob API.

Since:
0.2.25
